originalText.text: Best place to stop and rest up while on a quest. I stop by often to visit and get a healthy dose of blue food (especially the cookies and 7 layer dip!) Sally always makes me take some for the road, and I bring them back to camp. Some go into the fire for my dad (Apollo) since he loves the cookies so much. He sends Sally and Paul (and of course Estelle, who is guaranteed to one day rule the world) his best regards

originalText.text: Went to Sally's to learn more about a quest I was given by the Oracle with my friends. 10/10 would recommend, Sally's blue cookies and 7 layer dip are amazing. So welcoming and kind. This Percy kid wanted to hog the cookies though.

originalText.text: LOVE IT!!! Had to stop here during my quest (im a hepheastus kid) and ended up making a machine to replicate sally's cookies. However, the cookies it produces don't taste as good. I want to go back to try again, but chiron said i have to wait my turn."

originalText.text: I went on a side quest to Percy’s house. He wasn’t home but Sally was. She makes the best blue cookies and blue cakes and blueberry smoothies. 10/10 would recommend.
